    "Some researchers also used Hyperspectral Imaging (HSI) and DL models to more clearly observe plant disease signs in plant disease detection.",
    "A comprehensive assessment of the DL with the HSI approach was done (Signoroni et al. 2019).",
    "A thorough evaluation of many DL models, including 2D-CNN, LSTM/GRU, and a hybrid LSTM/GRU having 2D-CNN, was conducted to prevent overfitting and boost accuracy.",
